body_html: Eigen will not print error messages to stderr when it fails to initialize the CUDA runtime (see https://bitbucket.org/eigen/eigen/commits/8bfe1ed866fbd09954d65a644584ce5d1f741aa7 for details). If you pull the latest version of TensorFlow from github and return your model you should get some information to help pinpoint the root cause of the issue.
